# hubot-android-os-usage
Check Android usage share (and check which one to target)

## Installing
`npm install hubot-android-os-usage`

## Example usage
```js
var hubot-android-os-usage = require('hubot-android-os-usage');

// Do whatever you want with 'hubot-android-os-usage'!
```
